    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Hunting! 是一款以管理和培养新英雄为重点的回合制策略RPG。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请训练英雄们，使其能够参加最后的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >英雄管理</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras/4fd136446d77aaa8eb7b3b4aaf765831.avif?t=1750933861\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras_big/4fd136446d77aaa8eb7b3b4aaf765831.avif?t=1750933861 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雇佣未完成的英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然后通过训练，将他们打造为完整的团队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索与战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras/cb25f0c99b3d36e4be0d13a0dccd9e41.avif?t=1750933861\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras_big/cb25f0c99b3d36e4be0d13a0dccd9e41.avif?t=1750933861 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了达成目标，请探索各个区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索的过程中，您将与英雄们一起，在基于短暂SRPG的战斗系统中与众多敌人战斗。</p>",
